    "Details": "The Arbalest 2, introduced in 3079 removes one of the LRM-10 launchers to add a MASC system. In doing this the 'Mech is capable of disengaging from an enemy that may be beyond its combat capabilities much easier than the standard Arbalest.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.02</color></b>",
